{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-works-work-js","path":"/tartun/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"efe0b525-3e78-55ea-9ca2-b82f8c310947","excerpt":"Project Description Tartun (Tarik Tunai) is a mobile app that enables cash withdrawals and transfers through an mPOS Cashlez device…","html":"<h2>Project Description</h2>\n<p><strong>Tartun (Tarik Tunai)</strong> is a mobile app that enables cash withdrawals and transfers through an <strong>mPOS Cashlez device</strong> — letting anyone run a cash-withdrawal point from their home or existing business.</p>\n<h2>What I did</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Built the cash withdrawal and transfer features by integrating the Flip.id API with Java Servlets</li>\n<li>Developed the Android app UI and integrated it with the backend</li>\n<li>Built the web admin with JSP, JavaScript, and CSS on PostgreSQL 12</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Tartun ( Tarik Tunai )","category":"Mobile & Web Development","tags":["Java 8","Java Servlet","PostgreSQL","Android","JSP","mPOS"],"description":"A mobile app for cash withdrawals and transfers through an mPOS Cashlez device, with a web admin behind it.","projectLink":"https://tartun.explorewisata.id","date":"2021.10.04","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.6216216216216217,"src":"/static/8ae25edd9efe4494e47cb47a6e5c6d7c/73f08/image.png","srcSet":"/static/8ae25edd9efe4494e47cb47a6e5c6d7c/57fc3/image.png 300w,\n/static/8ae25edd9efe4494e47cb47a6e5c6d7c/f8eb5/image.png 600w,\n/static/8ae25edd9efe4494e47cb47a6e5c6d7c/73f08/image.png 1200w,\n/static/8ae25edd9efe4494e47cb47a6e5c6d7c/35e16/image.png 1588w","sizes":"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tartun/","fileNo":3}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}